Description:
Perfect family home in fantastic location
Built by Dennis Family Homes in 2008, this 4 bedroom home comprises 21.7sqs of living making it ideal for the active family. With three separate living areas that can each be zoned off from one another, this home is ideal for ensuring each member of the family have their own space. The contemporary style kitchen has stainless steel appliances with direct access from the double garage and alfresco entertaining area. All four bedrooms are generous in size with the master bedroom enjoying ensuite and walk in robe. The family bathroom has the added luxury of a spa bath. This home has an abundance of storage with walk in linen, walk in pantry and built in robes to the remaining bedrooms. Climate throughout is controlled by gas ducted heating and evaporative air conditioning. Externally there is a double garage with remotes, rear yard access and a double size garden shed on an 800sqm. Why would you build, when this home has everything you need!

Quiet Court Location

The other three bedrooms are located together with the family bathroom and laundry and comprise built in robes. This top quality low maintenance house is sited on a generous 769 square metre corner block in a prime river end location, offering easy caravan/boat access to rear yard. Appealing kitchen/meals area with quality stainless steel appliances and timber doors opening to a lovely private courtyard, perfect for outdoor entertaining. Separate lounge, three generous bedrooms, impressive ensuite and bathroom. Spacious laundry with excellent storage and direct house access from double garage. Extensive veggie patch and appealing low maintenance surrounds. Presents in excellent condition, prime location, only a short walk to Murray River. Inspection will impress!
